title: Prosciutto & Fontina Panini With Arugula Pesto And Pickled Shal
summary: You can never have too many main course recipes, so give Prosciutto & Fontina Panini With Arugula Pesto And Pickled Shal a try. This recipe serves 4 and costs $7.83 per serving. One portion of this dish contains about 62g of protein, 71g of fat, and a total of 1507 calories. 3 people were glad they tried this recipe. From preparation to the plate, this recipe takes around 31 minutes. If you have arugula, slather the other of bread, cider vinegar, and a few other ingredients on hand, you can make it. All things considered, we decided this recipe deserves a spoonacular score of 69%. This score is good. Similar recipes include Prosciutto And Fontina Panini With Arugula Pesto, Prosciutto, Fontina, and Fig Panini, and Panini with Prosciutto, Fontina, Spinach and Slow-Roasted Tomatoes.
